summary: Adds a Small Village outside Whiterun, wouldn\'t reccomend download yet, but should be playable very soon.
descriptionHtml:
Adds a Small Village outside Whiterun, wouldn\'t reccomend download yet, but should be playable very soon.

Unfortunately, I lost interest in this project and therefore have moved on to something else, If anyone would like to download this and finish it themselves, that is absolutely fine, just give the new file back to me and I will upload it giving you and anyone else who contributed full credit for the project and will give you admin / editing rights on this page. However until the time comes where someone would like to finish this project off, It is going to be discontinued.
author: Sam Beevors
